name: Gather Community Plant #022 - Devnull
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their rendition of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

devnull is a generative artist who creates simplistically styled works that are soothing to the eye on FxHash.

"More often than not, I start with one idea but end up with something completely different. I love the element of surprise, playing with parameters, modifying values way beyond their sensible range of inputs just to see what happens. " - devnull
